Yeah, it's pretty well. We talked about this in our talk a few years back in PyCon.

00:12:11.244 --> 00:12:18.244
How, like, you can tell a story with a table or you can communicate data in a better way, you know.

00:12:19.550 --> 00:12:24.750
not a more optimized way, but a more legible way, where like, your main point is like, describe

00:12:24.750 --> 00:12:31.070
like a title and a subtitle. And you have notes at the bottom. And you can guide people through

00:12:31.070 --> 00:12:35.869
